Block A — Create the Global Choice "Ownership Type"
This is the choice object (the option set), not yet attached to any column. We'll attach it in Block B.
Steps

Open Power Apps maker portal (make.powerapps.com) in the EMS environment
Left nav: Solutions → open the EMS solution where the existing tables live (the same solution that holds pei_bptobumapping)
Inside the solution: top bar + New → More → Choice

A "New choice" panel opens on the right.
Fields to set
FieldValueNotesDisplay nameOwnership TypeHuman-readable labelNamepei_ownershiptypeLogical/schema name. Important: type this all lowercase explicitly — don't rely on auto-derivation, which may capitalize. Save-before-rename lesson per ADR-049 applies to choices too.External Name(leave blank / auto)Not used in this projectDescriptionPer ADR-040: classifies a Parent Business Process as BU-owned, Horizontal, or Unresolved. Used on pei_bptobumapping table to drive Control Procedure BU inheritance via L1-A09.Helpful for future devs
The three Items (option values)
Click + Add new item three times. For each, set Label, Value, and optionally Color:
LabelValueColor (optional)BU-owned890920000Green or blue (any consistent choice)Horizontal890920001Purple or amberUnresolved890920002Grey/red
Critical: the Value field must be set explicitly to 890920000, 890920001, 890920002. Power Apps auto-assigns option values starting at some default; we want to lock these specific numbers because L1-A09's flow code (and any future code) will reference these numeric values, and they need to be predictable.
Save & publish

Click Save
Wait for the save toast confirmation
Top of the solution: click Publish all customizations (or just Publish for this choice)
Wait for the publish to complete (the spinner clears)

Verification before Block B
After save + publish, the new Choice should appear in the solution's Choices list (left nav inside the solution → Choices). Click it open and confirm:

Schema name shows as pei_ownershiptype (lowercase)
Three items are listed with the exact values 890920000 / 890920001 / 890920002
The labels match BU-owned / Horizontal / Unresolved
